\cf7 \cb3 \strokec7 1.\cf2 \strokec2  Executive Summary\cf2 \cb1 \strokec2 \
\
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 This project evaluates whether different prompting techniques improve LLM-based validation of clinical summary features relative to human validation.\cf2 \cb1 \strokec2 \
\
\cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 Independent Variable (IV)\cf2 \cb1 \strokec2 \
\
